5000|$|Guatemala is {{very popular}} for its archaeological sites, pre-Hispanic cities as well as tourist-religious centers like Basilica <b>of</b> <b>Esquipulas</b> and City <b>of</b> <b>Esquipulas</b> and also the {{beautiful}} beaches on the Pacific and Atlantic coasts of Guatemala. Other tourist destinations are the National Parks and others [...] such as the Maya Biosphere Reserve.|$|R
